data.title: All About Knapp
data.meta_description:
All About Knapp - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. - The document is a 55,167 word account written in English and Spanish detailing the Knapp saga by Alfredo Juillet Frascara from 2007-2012. 
- It provides summaries of 40 chapters/stories set in the Knapp planetary system between the years 3478-5660 involving characters such as Gefuhl Konslo, Rixia, and Professor Worsof.  
- The first story, Knapp 1, takes place on the planet Lorinata where the main character Gefuhl becomes lost in the jungle and encounters prehistoric creatures before finding his way to the city of Oredloro.
